data.description: ***ATTENTION HOMEBUYERS*** Now offering a full 1% interest rate reduction for the first 12 months at no cost to the buyer when using preferred lender. ***SAVE THOUSANDS IN THE 1ST YEAR!!!***CALL FOR DETAILS*****HUGE PRICE REDUCTION PLUS SELLER TO PAY CLOSING COSTS UP TO 3%, with reasonable offer** Run, don't walk! Welcome to this beautifully maintained home nestled in the heart of Seminole, Florida. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience - ideal for anyone seeking a serene living experience. With 4 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths, this home offers 2 additional extra rooms that can fulfill your spacing needs several ways -  bedrooms, game rooms, nursery, or an office space - the options are endless. The galley kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances (2023) and a direct view to your awesome backyard. The gorgeous heated pool and travertine deck will amaze you! No yard work in the back as you find beautiful turf and newer vinyl fencing. Minutes away from top-rated schools, Seminole City Park, shopping centers, and fine dining options. Just a baseball player's stone throw to Florida’s stunning beaches and scenic nature trails. Many aspects of this home have been recently updated...it's just waiting for you and your belongings! Hurricane windows 2021, (2) HVAC 2022 - all ductwork completely replaced as well, Roof 2013 (partial roof with addition is 2022),
